results.name: T(n,k) is the number of connected unlabeled posets with n elements and rank k: triangle read by rows.
comment: This is a variant of A263859 admitting only connected posets.
link: Index entries for sequences related to posets
formula: T(n,0) = 0 for k>0; due to the connectivity constraint.
T(n,n-1) = 1; the poset with elements in a single chain.
